<!-- Application Guidelines -->
<div class="container accent-bg">
  <div class="wrapper flow">
    <h2 class="center">Application Guidelines</h2>
    <p>
      <b>A Few Things to Keep in Mind</b>
    </p>
    <p>
      This is a space for reflection.<br />
      You may write about a question, a return, a pause, or a continuation.
    </p>
    <p>
      This is a self-directed residency.<br />
      The structure is intentionally light, allowing your practice to unfold in its own rhythm.
    </p>
    <p>
      There are no prescribed ways of responding.<br />
      You are welcome to write simply and directly, in your own language.
    </p>
    <p>
      Your responses may remain open or unresolved.<br />
      It is enough to articulate where you are, even if that place is still forming.
    </p>
    <p>
      Clarity is valued over length.<br />
      Please stay within the suggested word limits.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- A Note on Selection -->
<div class="container">
  <div class="wrapper flow">
    <h2 class="center">A Note on Selection</h2>
    <p>
      The residency hosts a limited number of participants each year.
    </p>
    <p>
      Selections are made with attention to:
      <ul>
        <li>clarity of intent</li>
        <li>depth of engagement with practice</li>
        <li>readiness for a self-directed process</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p>
      We also hold space for a diverse cohort across forms, geographies, and stages of practice.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- Before You Begin -->
<div class="container accent-bg">
  <div class="wrapper flow">
    <h2 class="center">Before you begin</h2>
    <p>
      You may wish to sit with these questions:
      <ul>
        <li>Why does this time feel necessary now?</li>
        <li>How do I relate to working without external direction?</li>
        <li>What might it mean to have uninterrupted time for dance</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
